    	&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;3.0.3&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="15048445" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 9 Dec 2015 10:30:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user mxm commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1441#issuecomment-163181852&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1441#issuecomment-163181852&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Not sure about the Kryo dependency in the root pom. We already pin the Kryo version via dependency management in the root pom. This eliminates most conflicts in sub projects. The proposed changes are a special solution for the flink-storm module which has conflicting transitive dependencies due to its dependency on Storm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Kryo version is 2.24.0. Where did you get the 3.0.3 from?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15048459" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 9 Dec 2015 10:41:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user StephanEwen commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1441#issuecomment-163184620&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1441#issuecomment-163184620&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Fair enough, let&apos;s leave it specific to storm then.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Kryo beyond 2.24.0 changed maven group and artifact names...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15048471" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 9 Dec 2015 10:48:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user mxm commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1441#issuecomment-163186476&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1441#issuecomment-163186476&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    I&apos;m not really sure about the implications of Kryo in the root pom so I try to fix it where it is a problem first.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;gt;Kryo beyond 2.24.0 changed maven group and artifact names...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Ah I see. Let&apos;s update the Kryo version in a separate step.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
